      "date": "2012-06-24 17:00:04.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 6: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.2/x86_64, CentOS release 5.8/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/413a1d6a-be1a-11e1-841f-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
